{"tid":1418154,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽］前線行動檢討","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:35:57.000Z","uid":224104,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c3d276a772c747bc9ad194fbb9ee5ea8620349","tid":1418154,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我屌晒你地老母呀</strong></span></span><br />\n出面d兄弟仲打緊<br />\n街坊出去接放學 睇邊條路安全<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你班仆街係度檢乜撚野討？</span><br />\n前綫戀權？前線中計？失民意？<br />\n檢討係重要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但唔係當前綫仲係外面既時候做</span></span><br />\n一心諗住上嚟睇下有咩逃生路線<br />\n睇邊度要幫手<br />\n再唔係有咩新文宣 求救 或者片要backup<br />\n屌你老母全部係度開檢討會<br />\n重要同一段內容可以開幾個post<br />\n我理得你講得有幾精彩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚係打緊仗既時候講</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>齊上齊落</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"aab16bfce9febcacc6af7f3285e9ec5447869968","tid":1418154,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e1ad2064ddbbc9189146fae40eddfa9bdccd9b48","tid":1418154,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"90088efdc47848cf12a2f36cbd77d8a74f95cf28","tid":1418154,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2684ae3e9be461354eb4f557fc363d5870d30c8b","tid":1418154,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:51.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"d3711794edda1fc7d4cd97654255eae57a376d83","tid":1418154,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:01:01.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"8f579fb6fb40001ab5a11c4cd2998d10e6d55886","tid":1418154,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0